   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>Aurelius Horos and Koprion, collectors of grain taxes of the village of Philadelphia in the Arsinoite nome, to Aurelii Sarapion and Mestas, comarchs of the village of Philadelphia. I have received from you eighteen artabai of barley, equal 18. Year 4 of our lord Probus Augustus, Mesore 26.</ab>
